@startuml EditCourses
|Admin|
start
:1. Open course list;
:2. Select course to edit;
:3. Open edit form with current data;
:4. Modify course details;
:5. Submit changes;
|CourseDashboard|
:6. Validate new data;
|CourseController|
:7. Update course in backend;
|Database|
:8. Save updated record;
|CourseController|
:9. Return success;
|CourseDashboard|
:10. Display confirmation;
:11. Refresh course list;
stop
@enduml
